541859a2fb7042d63594a35937743dc2a9fecc9","tid":837482,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三國將在11月在日內瓦舉行WTO理事會時提案，要求強化相關規則以提高補助金的透明度；面對會員國忽視通報責任，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議導入新的處罰措施舉體的措施可能包括不得出任WTO議長職務、增加分擔金負擔等</span>。</blockquote><br />\n一早應該咁做喇<br />\n不過照支那死性一定出古惑, 直接踢出組織或者自己起新朵唔摻班生番玩好過"},{"pid":"6ff3106836ce51551b20501b1e795f5f17f3582d","tid":837482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e30c99c9e0b2db93e78696d8eda796e40edbf48","tid":837482,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}